answers.answer: What is the 24 hour urine test?  What are they testing for?
I have to much protein in my urine

How far along are you? I had extreme preeclampsia with my previous pregnancies and protein in my urine was the first sign. I was put on bed rest to keep my blood pressure under control. This usually shows up in the mid-late second trimester. Don't freak yourself out I'm sure your doctor has a plan or you would've been asked to be seen immediately. I pray all is well. Blessings to you and your baby.

Just because u have protein in ur urine dont mean u have preclampsia I have protein in my urnie also but my bp is normal they just monitor baby closely and I got to the doctor three times a week...just keep clam mommy baby will be ok good luck!!!
